@startuml
title BP-23 - Invoice Generation

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Platform|
start
:Receive valid checkout or payment order request;
:Group selected bills for one school tenant;
:Generate invoice number;
:Attach selected obligations as invoice lines;
:Calculate total payable amount;

if (Invoice total valid?) then (Yes)
  :Persist invoice or payment order representation;
else (No)
  :Return invoice calculation error;
  stop
endif

|Parent Guardian|
:Receive invoice summary;
:Proceed to payment method selection;
stop

note right
Source of truth includes Invoice.
Current MVP represents this process through PaymentOrder.
A dedicated Invoice module is future scope.
end note
@enduml
